<plot>In this intimate and moving portrait we take a Walk of Wisdom with Mae Chee Sansanee Sthirasuta, the revered female spiritual leader of Thailand. For the first time, this compassionate Buddhist nun shares her life, her work and wisdoms and takes us on a breathtaking journey from her former days as a top model to her every day of helping others and living a life of peace and true beauty that really does come from the heart.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?018011</url></doc>
